meanings.definition: Kiahsville is an unincorporated community in Wayne County, West Virginia, United States.
meanings.english_definition: An unincorporated community in Wayne County, West Virginia, United States.

examples.sentence: Kiahsville is located along West Virginia Route 37, near the Twelvepole Creek.
